title: Watch: Suzy And Park Won Melt Hearts With Their Sweet Vocals In “Don’t Wait For Your Love” MV
text:
Shares 341 Display.Sharethrough.Soompi.1x1 
The music video for Suzy and Park Won’s soothing duet song “Don’t Wait For Your Love” was released on February 28! 
In the video, Suzy is looking beautiful as she shares eye contact with Park Won, who smoothly showcases his guitar skills.
